T02TD1959E:90a-0: @90a * // dpal gshin rje gshed nag po'i 'khor lo bri ba'i cho ga bzhugs //
T02TD1959E:90a-2: * // bcom ldan 'das gshin rje gshed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1959E:90a-3: don dam chos sku zhi ba nyid //
T02TD1959E:90a-4: gang 'dir khams gsum rnam rgyal te //
T02TD1959E:90a-5: gshin rje'i sgra zhes grag pa yi /'khor lo bskor ba'i cho ga bshad //
T02TD1959E:90a-6: yon tan ldan pa'i sngags pa ni //
T02TD1959E:90a-7: cho ga bzhin du bsnyen pa yis //
T02TD1959E:90a-8: dur khrod dben pa la sogs par //
T02TD1959E:90a-9: mandala khru do'i chad du bya //
T02TD1959E:90a-10: dri dang ba yi rnam lnga pa dang //
T02TD1959E:90a-11: nyi zla sogs par byi dor bya //
T02TD1959E:90a-12: ba lang sha sogs dam rdzas lnga //
T02TD1959E:90a-13: gzhan yang tshogs kyi 'khor lo dang //
T02TD1959E:90a-14: phyi nang mchod pa'i bye brag gis //
T02TD1959E:90a-15: legs par mchod pa byas nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90a-16: 'khor lo bri dang btu ba dang /
T02TD1959E:90a-17: drang dang bsre dang sngo ba bsam //
T02TD1959E:90a-18: sngags pa rnal 'byor ldan pa yis //
T02TD1959E:90a-19: lho yi phyogs su kha bltas te //
T02TD1959E:90a-20: dam tshig rjes su dran pa yis //
T02TD1959E:90a-21: aom badzra sa ma ya ste /
T02TD1959E:90a-22: gsang sngags 'di ni dran byed cing //
T02TD1959E:90a-23: 'khor lo bri ba brtsam par bya //
T02TD1959E:90a-24: dbus na sor tshad bcu drug par //
T02TD1959E:90a-25: kun du zlum por bskor ba ni //
T02TD1959E:90a-27: rim pa gsum du bskor ba la //
T02TD1959E:90a-28: sgo med lcags mkhar bcu drug bya //
T02TD1959E:90a-29: 'di ni gshin rje'i grong khyer te //
T02TD1959E:90a-30: srid pa gsum gyi 'jug sa yin //
T02TD1959E:90a-31: de yi phyi rim mu khyud gsum //
T02TD1959E:90a-32: kun du lcags ris bskor ba ste //
T02TD1959E:90a-33: mu khyud de dag re re yang //
T02TD1959E:90a-34: khang pa bcu drug dag dang ldan //
T02TD1959E:90a-35: 'gro ba'i chos bzhin gcod pa yi //
T02TD1959E:90a-37: phyi rol mu khyud tha ma la //
T02TD1959E:90a-38: yi ge ka sogs da yig mtha' //
T02TD1959E:90a-39: nga nya bsal nas dgod par bya //
T02TD1959E:90a-40: yi ge dha sogs ksha yig mtha' //
T02TD1959E:90a-41: de yi rjes su bri bar bya //
T02TD1959E:90a-42: mu khyud dbus ma de la ni //
T02TD1959E:90a-43: dbyangs yig bcu drug gnyis 'gyur dgod //
T02TD1959E:90a-44: btung dang dgod sogs brtsam pa na //
T02TD1959E:90b-0: mtshan ma 'di dag @90b shes par bya //
T02TD1959E:90b-1: zla ba mig dang yon tan dang //
T02TD1959E:90b-2: rig byed mda' dang dbang po dang //
T02TD1959E:90b-3: rgya mtsho bkra shis gza' dang phyogs //
T02TD1959E:90b-4: grags pa nyi ma yan lag sa //
T02TD1959E:90b-5: tshes zhes bya bar rab tu grags //
T02TD1959E:90b-6: phyi rol mu khyud tha ma la //
T02TD1959E:90b-7: shar gyi changs thig nas brtsams te //
T02TD1959E:90b-8: rim min gza' can khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-9: yi ge bkra shis can blangs te /
T02TD1959E:90b-10: nang gi ngos kyi mu khyud kyi //
T02TD1959E:90b-11: tshangs pa'i thig gi ngos dag la //
T02TD1959E:90b-12: phyogs bzhir mig gi tshad du sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-13: rim min phyogs can khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-14: yi ge mig gi tshad blangs te //
T02TD1959E:90b-15: shar du de yi g-yas g-yon gzhag / rim min bkra shis khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-16: dbyangs yig gnyis pa can blangs nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-17: mig gi tshad du byas nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-18: de yi ngos la re re gzhag / shar gyi tshang thig nas bgrangs pa'i //
T02TD1959E:90b-19: rgya mtsho can gyi khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-20: dbyangs yig bcu gcig pa dang ldan //
T02TD1959E:90b-21: mig gi tshang du blangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-22: lho yi ngos la de bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-23: shar nas rim pa bzhin pa yid //
T02TD1959E:90b-24: zla ba can gyi khyim nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-25: dbyangs yig bcu gsum pa dang ldan //
T02TD1959E:90b-26: lho ru de yi rjes sbyin bya //
T02TD1959E:90b-27: dha nyid dbyangs yig gsal ba ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-28: mig gi tshad du blangs byas la //
T02TD1959E:90b-29: sngon bzhin du nub kyi phyogs su sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-30: shar nas bkra shis khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-31: dbyangs yig bcu gsum pa dang ldan mig gi tshad du blangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-32: nub kyi ngos su de bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-33: shar brtsams tshes can khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-34: dbyangs yig bcu gcig dang ldan pa //
T02TD1959E:90b-35: mig gi tshad du blangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-36: byang gi ngos su de bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-37: rlung gi sa bon zhes bya ba //
T02TD1959E:90b-38: mig ji tshad blangs de rjes sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-39: mda' tsan khang pa na gnas pa //
T02TD1959E:90b-40: 'od kyi gong bur byas pa dang //
T02TD1959E:90b-41: de nyid nas ni bgrang ba yi //
T02TD1959E:90b-42: gza' can khang pa la gnas pa //
T02TD1959E:90b-43: dbyangs yig gsum pa dang ldan pa dag //
T02TD1959E:90b-44: zla ba'i tshad du blangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-45: byang shar mtshams su re re sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-46: rgya mtsho'i khang pa na gnas pa //
T02TD1959E:90b-47: dbyangs yig gnyis pa dang ldan pa //
T02TD1959E:90b-48: rim min yon tan khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-49: zla ba'i tshad du bzung nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-50: shar lho mtshams su de bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1959E:90b-51: rim min bkra shis khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-52: dbyangs yig lnga pa ldan pa dang //
T02TD1959E:90b-53: yan lag can gyi khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:90b-54: zla ba'i tshad du blangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:90b-55: lho nub mtshams su de bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1959E:91a-0: @91a * // rim min tshes can khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:91a-1: dbyangs yig gsum pa ldan pa dang //
T02TD1959E:91a-2: rim min bkra shis khang pa nas //
T02TD1959E:91a-3: zla ba'i tshad du blangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-4: nub byang mtshams su de bzhin sbyin //
T02TD1959E:91a-5: de ltar dgod pa byas nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-6: de nas drang ba brtsam par bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-7: dam tshig rjes su dran byed cing //
T02TD1959E:91a-8: rdo rje shugs dang ldan pa yis //
T02TD1959E:91a-9: shar gyi tshangs thig ngos gnyis nas //
T02TD1959E:91a-10: yi ge zung ldan drangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-11: dbus kyi khang par gzhag par bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-12: phyogs gzhan tshangs thig ngos dag nas //
T02TD1959E:91a-13: de bzhin zung ldan dangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-14: de bzhin dbus kyi khang par gzhag / de nas shar gyi yi ge yang //
T02TD1959E:91a-15: zung ldan gnyis pa drangs nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-16: rim pa gnyis pa'i khang par gzhag / phyogs gzhan du yang de bzhin no //
T02TD1959E:91a-17: shar gyi zung ldan gsum pa yang //
T02TD1959E:91a-18: rim pa gsum pa'i khang par drangs //
T02TD1959E:91a-19: phyogs gzhan du yang de bzhin no //
T02TD1959E:91a-20: mtshams kyi yi ge ya bral ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-21: rang rang nang ni mtshams su drang //
T02TD1959E:91a-22: de dag byung ba khang stong du //
T02TD1959E:91a-23: dbyangs kyi yi ge drang bar bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-24: dbyangs kyi yi ge'i gzhi la ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-25: ming gi yi ge drang bar bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-26: ming gi yi ge'i gzhi la ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-27: so so'i las dang mthun pa yi //
T02TD1959E:91a-28: bskul ba'i yi ge dgod par bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-29: bsad dang bskrad dang dbye ba la //
T02TD1959E:91a-30: yi ge phat ni gzhag par bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-31: mnan pa la ni yi ge lam //
T02TD1959E:91a-32: zhi ba la ni yi ge aom //
T02TD1959E:91a-33: rgyas pa la ni yi ge sv'a //
T02TD1959E:91a-34: dbang la ho: yis brgyan pa ste //
T02TD1959E:91a-35: dgug pa la ni yi ge dza: //
T02TD1959E:91a-36: de la las kyi 'od zer ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-37: zhi la chu ste rgyas las //
T02TD1959E:91a-38: dbang gi me ste drag po'i rlung //
T02TD1959E:91a-39: dbye dgug bskrad pa drag dang mthun //
T02TD1959E:91a-40: mnan pa dag gi rgyas pa bzhin //
T02TD1959E:91a-41: drang ba'i sbyor ba byas nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91a-42: bsre ba'i sbyor ba brtsam par bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-43: gnyis med sngags dang ldan pa yis //
T02TD1959E:91a-44: dbus kyi yi ge bkra shis la'ang //
T02TD1959E:91a-45: zla ltar 'od kyi gong bur bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-46: 'od kyi gong bu de'i nang du //
T02TD1959E:91a-47: 'dod pa'i bsgrub bya gzhag par bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-48: de dkyil rang min dang por gzhag / phyogs kyi khyim na gnas pa yi ;
T02TD1959E:91a-49: / yi ge zur ma thams cad kyang //
T02TD1959E:91a-50: de tshe 'od kyi gong bur bya //
T02TD1959E:91a-51: sngags kyi rgyal po bcu pa yang //
T02TD1959E:91a-52: bcu drug khyim du spel te bri //
T02TD1959E:91a-53: byin rlob h'um zhes bya ba yang //
T02TD1959E:91a-54: khang pa bzhi la zur rer mdzes //
T02TD1959E:91a-55: yongs su dag par bkod byas te //
T02TD1959E:91a-56: mchod dang gtor ma byas nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91b-0: spro ba dag ni brtsam @91b par bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-1: las kyi dbye ba ji lta bar //
T02TD1959E:91b-2: 'khor lo'i ras ni blang bya ste //
T02TD1959E:91b-3: zhi ba dang ni rgyas pa la //
T02TD1959E:91b-4: shin tu dge ba'i ras las bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-5: dbang dgug smad 'tshong smad dkris sogs //
T02TD1959E:91b-6: bsad dang dbye dang bskrad pa dang //
T02TD1959E:91b-7: mnan pa la ni dur khrod ras //
T02TD1959E:91b-8: gi wam gur kum zhi rgyas la //
T02TD1959E:91b-9: dbang dang dgug la tsandan dmar //
T02TD1959E:91b-10: mnan pa la ni ldong ros sogs //
T02TD1959E:91b-11: bskrad la bya rog khrag gis te //
T02TD1959E:91b-12: dbye la rta dang ma he sogs //
T02TD1959E:91b-13: bsad la dug la sogs pa bri //
T02TD1959E:91b-14: dge ba'i las la shing bzang po //
T02TD1959E:91b-15: dge ba min la rus pa dang //
T02TD1959E:91b-16: lcags la sogs pas bri bar bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-17: zhi la shar blta dbang la nub ;
T02TD1959E:91b-18: / rgyas pa byang ste drag po lho //
T02TD1959E:91b-19: gzhan yang ci rigs par sbyar bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-20: zhi rgyas dbang dang dgug pa la //
T02TD1959E:91b-21: sa skor rim bzhin bkod byas te //
T02TD1959E:91b-22: gnam skor dag ni rim las bzlog / bsad bskrad dbye dang mnan pa la //
T02TD1959E:91b-23: sa skor rim la bzlog pa ste //
T02TD1959E:91b-24: gnam skor dag ni rim bzhin bri ;
T02TD1959E:91b-25: /'di ltar legs par ma bris na //
T02TD1959E:91b-27: de bas 'bad de nan tan bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-28: ras kyi 'khor lo legs zin nas //
T02TD1959E:91b-30: ras kyi 'khor lor spyan drangs te //
T02TD1959E:91b-31: rdo rje bsdu ba'i sbyor ba yis //
T02TD1959E:91b-33: ras kyi 'khor lo mchod nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91b-34: bden pa'i byin rlabs dmigs par bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-35: ji ltar gsungs pa'i cho ga bzhin //
T02TD1959E:91b-36: 'khor lo sba ba byas nas ni //
T02TD1959E:91b-37: gsang sngags bzlog pa brtsam par bya //
T02TD1959E:91b-38: aom badzra sa ma ya stvam /
T02TD1959E:91b-40: aom badzra be ga rdo rje shugs kyi sngags so //
T02TD1959E:91b-41: aom aa sa me tri ma h'a sa ma ye sv'a h'a /
T02TD1959E:91b-42: yi ge bsre ba'i sngags so //
T02TD1959E:91b-43: aom badzra sa ma na dza: dz'a /
T02TD1959E:91b-45: aom ya ma r'a dza sa do me ya /
T02TD1959E:91b-46: ya me do ru na yo da ya /
T02TD1959E:91b-49: yakshe yatstsha ni r'a ma ya phat phat /
T02TD1959E:91b-50: 'di ni rtsa ba'i gsang sngags te /
T02TD1959E:91b-52: aom hr'i: shtri: wi kri t'a na na h'um h'um phat phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1959E:91b-53: 'di ni las kyi sngags te las thams cad pa'o //
T02TD1959E:91b-58: ba sham ku ru sv'a h'a /
T02TD1959E:91b-60: m'a ra ya phat gsad pa'i'o //
T02TD1959E:91b-61: bi dve sha ya phat dbye ba'i'o //
T02TD1959E:92a-2: a'a karsha ya h'um dza: dgug pa'i'o //
T02TD1959E:92a-4: a'a li k'a li'i grong khyer ni //
T02TD1959E:92a-5: gsang sngags 'byung ba brtsam pa ste //
T02TD1959E:92a-6: las kyi btson ra dag kyang yin //
T02TD1959E:92a-7: yi ge btu ba med na ni //
T02TD1959E:92a-8: gsang sngags sgra ni log par 'gyur //
T02TD1959E:92a-9: yi ge tshad par ma bkod na //
T02TD1959E:92a-10: gsang sngags sgra ni nyams par 'gyur //
T02TD1959E:92a-11: gsang sngags brda yis ma bstan na //
T02TD1959E:92a-12: sngags pa'i dngos grub med par 'gyur //
T02TD1959E:92a-13: drang ba dag ni ma byas na //
T02TD1959E:92a-15: yi ge bsre ba ma byas na //
T02TD1959E:92a-16: khang pa bcu drug don med 'gyur //
T02TD1959E:92a-17: bskor phyogs log na don mi 'grub //
T02TD1959E:92a-18: rig sngags nyams dang log pa ni //
T02TD1959E:92a-19: lha min g-yul las pham pa dang //
T02TD1959E:92a-20: dbang po'i dgra bo bsad pa bzhin //
T02TD1959E:92a-21: 'khor lo spo ba ma byas na //
T02TD1959E:92a-22: cho ga dag ni nyams par 'gyur //
T02TD1959E:92a-23: rgyu yin pa dang sbyor ba dang //
T02TD1959E:92a-25: de bas nan tan bskyed de bya ;
T02TD1959E:92a-26: / dpal gshin rje gshed nag po'i 'khor lo bri ba'i cho ga rdzogs so//
